{"tid":976133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【流感肆虐】廣州最少5宗壞死性腦炎 北京疾控澄清：病毒\"未\"出現變異","createTime":"2019-01-10T07:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T08:35:28.000Z","uid":65346,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"69d2cbc5d40e56392f9e2c30fdc113d762687a0d","tid":976133,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:42:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190110/59126051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190110%2F59126051&d=pNUid%2BJj0gUX5Bi3f5gA8wdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=bc9e0d3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190110%2F59126051&h=43430a5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190110/59126051</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n內地傳媒報道，雖然今年流感高峯期感染流感人數降低，但仍有不少重症出現。昨日，一篇〈緊急通知！流感轉向<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攻擊孩子腦部</span>，廣州已出現5例<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">壞死</span>性腦炎〉文章在微博朋友圈熱傳，《南方都市報》昨日亦有作出相關報道，但北京疾控中心隨後表示，流感病毒目前未出現變異。<br />\n該文章稱，雖然今年流感的流行程度大大降低，但降低的是總體感染人數，實際感染流感的患者依然有一定比率發展為重症。「與以往的甲型H1N1病毒喜歡攻擊患兒肺部不同，今年的病毒更喜歡攻擊孩子的神經系統。」廣州市婦女兒童醫療中心證實已接收5宗<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">壞死</span>性腦炎的病童。<br />\n內媒日前訪問廣州市婦女兒童醫療中心內科副主任、感染科主任徐翼教授，他表示內科感染病區已擠滿患有流感的病童，跟以往甲型H1N1病毒喜歡<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攻擊患者肺部</span>不同，今年的病毒不時攻擊兒童的神經系統。<br />\n北京疾控中心接受《新京報》訪問時表示，北京仍處於流感高峯期，流感病原學監測結果顯示，目前為甲型H1N1流感病毒和甲型H3N2亞型流感病毒共同流行，以甲型H1N1流感病毒活動為主，目前未發現有流感<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">病毒變異</span>的情況。<br />\n北京疾控中心又指，雖然北京處於流感高峯期，但總體強度低於去年水平。未來一段時期內，流感活動度將會繼續維持在高水平，由流感病毒導致的流感病例將會增多，預計將持續至<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1月</span>中下旬。<br />\n《新京報》/《南方都市報》"},{"pid":"1b57d7975acf066480e518356729670a933e7098","tid":976133,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:45:18.000Z","msg":"點解係廣州唔係深圳呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者北京都好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31fb8038499b8cba18e97a33f39ca8e41123fb2","tid":976133,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b57d7975acf066480e518356729670a933e7098","tid":976133,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:45:18.000Z","msg":"點解係廣州唔係深圳呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者北京都好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:49:39.000Z","msg":"你放心...火車站好多人流...<br />\n羅湖同落馬洲可能已經入香港了...我講 d &quot;人入境 &quot;"},{"pid":"6bd1b73f01b497af4845080d001860618a7538fa","tid":976133,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b57d7975acf066480e518356729670a933e7098","tid":976133,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:45:18.000Z","msg":"點解係廣州唔係深圳呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者北京都好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:57:50.000Z","msg":"廣州大把北佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be44754f5bd59cc5b10b42dcbfebf7ec1e719a5e","tid":976133,"uid":65686,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大陸春運"},{"pid":"f3c1349ff0e098d688241ebf31624f23c801c6ab","tid":976133,"uid":49370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi